				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Shadowheart confides in the player during the third night that they stop to camp. The expected effects of their tadpole condition have not come to pass, and Shadowheart tries to reason what this might mean. Are they out of the woods, or is this still just the start of something much worse? Hope and disquiet in equal parts. "
